&gt;&gt; Catherine Kerst: Would you
call it a dance drama format?

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:50.510
&gt;&gt; Anuradha Nehru: And, the other
characteristic for, yes, very,

00:05:50.510 --> 00:05:55.140
very important feature of Kuchipudi
is Kuchipudi's history, rather,

00:05:55.140 --> 00:05:58.380
is that it is a dance drama form.

00:05:58.380 --> 00:06:02.760
It was a dance drama
form 500 years ago,

00:06:02.760 --> 00:06:08.820
and only in the past 70 years
or so, because of gurus.

00:06:08.820 --> 00:06:11.350
My guru, Guru Vempati
Chinna Satyam and his guru,

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:16.630
Guru Lakshminarayana Sastry that
