00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:17.800
And, just to briefly explain the
most recent dance that we presented

00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:20.920
in celebration of our 25 years.

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:26.910
We did a new work called "Why We
Dance", and the new work revolved

00:09:26.910 --> 00:09:32.350
around the feelings and the
thoughts of the Kalanidhi dancers.

00:09:32.350 --> 00:09:37.350
