00:16:29.410 --> 00:16:33.800
to learn whatever he
had to impart to me.

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:37.140
But, we were never
encouraged to ask questions.

00:16:37.140 --> 00:16:43.080
We just had to be there and absorb
everything that he had to give us,

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:46.280
