just taking what is given to them.

00:16:51.650 --> 00:16:55.940
So, right from the very beginning,
they would ask questions.

00:16:55.940 --> 00:17:00.300
And, in the early years, it took
a while for me, it was, it was,

00:17:00.300 --> 00:17:03.420
in retrospect the best thing
that could have happened

00:17:03.420 --> 00:17:07.270
because I learned so
much more through having

00:17:07.270 --> 00:17:09.040
to answer those questions.

00:17:09.040 --> 00:17:16.060
I had to go back and understand
the art form at a much deeper level

00:17:16.060 --> 00:17:19.590
in order to teach them and in
order to answer their questions.

00:17:19.590 --> 00:17:21.480
So, I think that was
a big difference

00:17:21.480 --> 00:17:25.540
where asking questions seemed to be
the most natural thing for students

00:17:25.540 --> 00:17:29.850
in this country, and
teaching them required that.

00:17:29.850 --> 00:17:37.850 position:56%
And, I didn't, I didn't demand the
