itself in their actions.

00:17:54.270 --> 00:17:57.360
And, it took time, but,
over time, then they began

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:59.910
to realize the value
of their learning.

00:17:59.910 --> 00:18:05.230
It came from their heart rather
