00:30:28.880 --> 00:30:30.180
&gt;&gt; Anuradha Nehru: Yes, yes.

00:30:30.180 --> 00:30:35.400 position:56%
We took a work called "Rasa" which
was an exploration of the nine moods

00:30:35.400 --> 00:30:38.420
as described in the Natya Shastra,

00:30:38.420 --> 00:30:42.120
but these nine moods are
