is it starts with a concept.

01:06:00.700 --> 01:06:04.860
It starts with a concept,
and sometimes,

01:06:04.860 --> 01:06:13.260
the concept requires lyrics,
so then poetry is written

01:06:13.260 --> 01:06:16.280
to which revolves around
that concept.

01:06:16.280 --> 01:06:23.020
And, then, and then, I think at
that's the stage where I roughly,

01:06:23.020 --> 01:06:28.160
I have a rough sketch of how
I visualize each of the scenes

01:06:28.160 --> 01:06:30.030
or each of those concepts.

01:06:30.030 --> 01:06:35.760
And so, I write out the notes
for each of those concepts,

01:06:35.760 --> 01:06:39.040
and that is what I take
to the music composer.

01:06:39.040 --> 01:06:42.470
