music composer is a flutist,

01:07:02.700 --> 01:07:06.900
then he would create the
raw score on a flute.

01:07:06.900 --> 01:07:12.720
And, this last, last composer
was a singer, so he just sang.

01:07:12.720 --> 01:07:20.070
His voice was the raw score,
and based off of that raw score,

01:07:20.070 --> 01:07:25.700
we choreograph the whole work.

01:07:25.700 --> 01:07:30.300
